Author: _Pulltab_
Text: I am really struggling this week to control my eating. I had been in a heavy restriction cycle and between outing myself to my family and the holidays, I’ve been essentially shoving anything I can get my hands on in my face for the past 4 days.

Author: gkelleyr
Text: How long have you been out of control feeling? You can do this just take baby steps! I’m like day two of getting back in control and only overeating and not binging feels like a win on my way back to restriction
